{"tid":732090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓:中國消費品不安全, 特別是有孩子的家庭 不吃中國食材 不用中國生活用品","createTime":"2018-07-06T17:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T06:46:29.000Z","uid":119393,"like":109,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5e9d7acccbc27fd8931a300f95ab63b3a8d1c920","tid":732090,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cnnews.chosun.com/client/news/viw.asp?cate=C01&amp;mcate=M1001&amp;nNewsNumb=20180750070&amp;nidx=50071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnnews.chosun.com%2Fclient%2Fnews%2Fviw.asp%3Fcate%3DC01%26mcate%3DM1001%26nNewsNumb%3D20180750070%26nidx%3D50071&d=VBfUe0L1U1Z5uIZsl0533i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0ed193dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://cnnews.chosun.com/client/news/viw.asp?cate=C01&amp;mcate=M1001&amp;nNewsNumb=20180750070&amp;nidx=50071</a><br />\n<br />\n為采訪韓朝統一籃球賽而訪朝的韓國記者團報道稱，朝方有關人士向他們表示，朝鮮生產的消費品質量更勝於中國產。<br />\n<br />\n朝方有關人士稱：&ldquo;不僅食品，普通消費品如今國產也已經完全超越了中國產&rdquo;，&ldquo;特別是有孩子的家庭，不吃使用中國食材的食物。生活用品也不夠安全，所以不用中國產。不用中國產，不吃中國產。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n該有關人士還表示：&ldquo;我們認為我們（朝鮮）的東西更好&rdquo;，&ldquo;因為我們生產的東西質量更好，所以不再用中國產。中國產品質量不行，所以人民不會去購買。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"ef6c33353e194e887604cd33a27f23bba36a85b8","tid":732090,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c43a1db9f819362a8e28bb5a09b939484e8d86","tid":732090,"uid":87511,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:34:16.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏<br />\n啲国產三鹿奶粉又可以留返畀啲小蝗子飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284f5e1695bfb6e22cec8f206203b58b7afd9fa9","tid":732090,"uid":52358,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"23c43a1db9f819362a8e28bb5a09b939484e8d86","tid":732090,"uid":87511,"like":14